Customize System databases for each group.
This will allow to assign a root database folder for each existing group.
For best results:
- create a specific group;
- put only required users into the group and specify a different root folder for the database for this group.

Any user, belonging to this group will be working with data from this customized location.

This allows to have same database structures to be used by multiple business groups.

Database Template is a path to the existing sdb database to be used as a module.

